UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I wasn\'t going to believe it until I heard it from you, personally.  Already our scouts are trickling in with information that the Shattered Hand are in disarray without their precious drillmaster to tell them what to do.$B$BYou\'ve traveled a long road, $N.  I trust that you will accept this armor along with my thanks.  Wear it proudly, you\'ve earned it!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4,`DetailsEmote3`=1000,`DetailsEmote4`=1000 WHERE `entry`=10937;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11039;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11096;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='That\'s what I wanted to hear!  You\'ve got the stuff, $N, that\'s for sure!$B$BYou think maybe you could come back again tomorrow when we\'ve made more cluster bombs?  I\'d have you back out there right now, but my assistant, Feknut, isn\'t back from collecting more bat guano for them.$B$BI wonder what\'s taking him so long?',`OfferRewardEmote1`=11,`OfferRewardEmote2`=6 WHERE `entry`=11153;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Ugh, what\'s that smell? Ack, it\'s you! Well, I guess I did send you on a smelly job!$B$BThank you, $c. Don\'t worry, I\'ll get this stuff back to Petrov as soon as we get out of here.$B$B<Feknut yells out loud to the explorers.>$B$BYou hear that guys? Lets get the hell out of here!!!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=6,`OfferRewardEmote2`=15,`CompleteEmote`=6 WHERE `entry`=11154;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Good work! With any luck at all, the destruction of their egg clutches and whelps should drive off those fiery beasts and prevent that magical blaze from spreading.$B$BWait... what\'s that sound? It sounds like the beating of wings.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1 WHERE `entry`=11157;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Unfortunate that one predator must be used to put down another, but that is the natural order of things.$B$BPerhaps now the proto-drakes and their whelps can go back to living peacefully. Somehow I doubt it with the reawakening of the vrykul.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=33 WHERE `entry`=11182;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Malister beckons you closer and speaks in whispered tones.>$B$BI was worried that something like this might happen. I tried to dissuade the captain from this course of action, but he is a dwarf of action with a definite outlook on how things should proceed.$B$BLet us speak of the options left to us.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11187;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The mage-lieutenant sighs.>$B$BUnfortunate business to be certain. Well, what\'s done is done. With any luck the new whelps that grow to be drakes at Ember Clutch will not retain a memory of our shameful actions therein.$B$BAnd with a bit more luck, the boundaries of that magical forest will not continue to spread.$B$BHere, $N, please take this pittance from the treasury for all of your troubles. It\'s the least that we can do.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11188;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11199;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Nice!$B$BBut what\'s this about the stuff you found inside those tanks? Are you saying that the Forsaken are spraying a plague upon the vrykul down there?',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=6,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11202;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The ore gave you a strange feeling? Maybe we wnon\'t use that stuff after all.$B$B<Steelring looks at the stuff and takes a step back, changing the subject.>$B$BThose gems look really nice! I wonder what I can get for them? Of course, there are always repairs, and new stuff to be made.$B$BYou know, I\'ve really found working with you to be profitable. Take this... it\'s the least that I can do!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=6,`OfferRewardEmote2`=4,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`CompleteEmote`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11218;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I\'m indebted to you, $c. At least with most of the mules and equipment recovered, we can hope to rebuild our numbers soon.$B$BPlease, take this.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`RequestItemsText`='This is quite a blow to our efforts. I don\'t even want to know what they discovered down there.$B$BIt\'s enough to keep me awake at night just trying to imagine what it could be.',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11224;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Bless you child! With your help, the Light shines even in the darkest of places.$B$BPlease, take this as just compensation for your good deeds. I shall see to the salvation of those you freed; at least, those truly within the Light, and the Alliance, who returned here to the keep.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=2,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11231;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Good work, $N, and good riddance.$B$BBut, what you say about that place troubles me still, and I think our culling is not quite at an end!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11235;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The captain breathes a sigh of relief.>$B$BWell, that should take some of the pressure off of us.$B$B$N, time and again you have proven yourself invaluable to Westguard Keep and the Alliance at large. Pick something from the treasury, $g boy : girl;! It\'s the least we can do!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=2,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11236;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='$N, we can\'t let this come to pass!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=5,`RequestItemsText`='What?! Plans for an attack upon the keep?$B$BA FROST WYRM?!!!',`CompleteEmote`=5 WHERE `entry`=11237;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Wow, that horn is cold!$B$BOnce again you\'ve saved Westguard Keep from certain doom. What a curious $g man : woman; you are, $N. If only there were more of you.$B$BWell, this certainly calls for a reward. Which do you prefer?',`OfferRewardEmote1`=5,`OfferRewardEmote2`=6,`RequestItemsText`='Is the attack averted? Are the frost wyrm and its master destroyed?$B$BDid you retrieve the horn?',`CompleteEmote`=6,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11238;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The priest quietly mouths a benediction for you.>$B$BBless you, $N, you have answered my prayers. Stand proudly in the Light, chin held high with the knowledge that your actions were most holy!$B$BI\'m certain that the church\'s coffers can yield up something of use to you.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=2,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11239;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The sapper grumbles as if he wishes that you hadn\'t succeeded.>$B$BThe captain will be pleased to hear of your success.$B$BYou know, since you\'ve been such a good sport in dealing with this Whisper Gulch business, why don\'t you take your pick of one of these?',`OfferRewardEmote1`=4,`OfferRewardEmote2`=6,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11240;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent targeting, $g sir : ma\'am;! I\'ll have to remember to buy a round for the cannoneers back at the keep.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11245;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Well, $g sir : ma\'am;, I have to say that you went about that particular business with a bit of zeal.$B$B<The sergeant looks at you warily.>$B$BAnyway, if you don\'t mind, I\'ll be taking my machete back now. It looks dull and we wouldn\'t want you to accidentally slip and carve me up, too.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=274,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11246;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Very good, $g sir : ma\'am;. That couldn\'t have been done without your help.$B$BI\'m sure that the captain will be pleased with my report on the matter once we\'re done here.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11247;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='A pleasure to meet you, $g sir : ma\'am;! I look forward to working with you.$B$BSpeaking of which, we have a great deal to do.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=66,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11248;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes, $g my son : my daughter;, that is ominous-looking, and you obviously had the right of it.$B$BThank you for bringing this scroll to me. I am very keen to study its implications. If I were to hazard a guess, I would say that these vrykul have a way to transcend death; at least those that are worthy.$B$BBy defeating the Winterskorn thane, you proved him unworthy. The Light only knows what he would have become, and what terror he might have rained down upon us, had you not slain him.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=273,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`CompleteEmote`=6,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11249;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='That\'s unbelievably good news! I knew that you could pull it off, $N!$B$BAt least someone around here can produce results!$B$BWell, this calls for a reward. Go ahead, take your pick; the treasury is open to you.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=4,`OfferRewardEmote2`=2,`CompleteEmote`=6,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11250;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Captain Adams takes the plans from you.>$B$BI\'m glad you decided to come over. My advisors and I will need some time to study these plans. In the meantime, we can use all the help we can get!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`RequestItemsText`='Valgarde has not fallen? That\'s a surprise.$B$BMust be due to your help. It sure wasn\'t because of Keller.',`CompleteEmote`=6 WHERE `entry`=11291;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You have done well, $N. If we\'d had allies like you when the land first began to change, perhaps we might have been able to preserve some of what we\'ve lost.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1 WHERE `entry`=11316;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1 WHERE `entry`=11319;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Already I can sense the change within you.$B$BAre you ready for what comes next?',`OfferRewardEmote1`=6 WHERE `entry`=11322;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11325;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Garwal was not a worg at all! The thing you describe him turning into sounds a lot like a worgen!$B$BBut, Ulfang said that it came south from the Grizzly Hills? Odd. There aren\'t any worgen there.$B$BI thank you for helping to restore Ulfang to his proper place amongst his pack. Now we both will be able to sleep peacefully.$B$BPlease, you must accept this as a sign of gratitude.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=5,`OfferRewardEmote2`=6,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`RequestItemsText`='$N, you have returned. What news of Ulfang?',`CompleteEmote`=6,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11326;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Holy... what the hell?! Look at this stuff!$B$BWe need to get this back to the keep a.s.a.p.!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=5,`RequestItemsText`='That place looks like a nightmare. Vrykul or not, no one deserves to be the victim of the Royal Apothecary Society.$B$BGlad I\'m standing safely over here. You find that package yet?',`CompleteEmote`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11327;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Oh... hey, that\'sh different!$B$BOkay, let me shee that shtuff. I jusht love tinkering with alchemy!$B$BInteresting, interesting... here, I think I know jusht what to do. A little mixing of that with the jusht the right amount of thish.$B$BYou know, I think a little dash of this rotgut will help, too ...hic!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=5,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`CompleteEmote`=6,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11328;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Huh? Well that sucks! Darn, I made thingsh worsh. In fact, I think I perfected their plague for them ...hic!$B$B<Peppy grimaces and takes a huge gulp of whatever noxious brew she\'s been drinking.>$B$BWell, I wash hoping that it wouldn\'t come down to thish, but it looks like there\'sh no alternative ...hic.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=5,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11330;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes, $N, what is it now?$B$BWHAT?!! A Forsaken super plague that melts you in no time?$B$BYou oozed my vrykul prisoner?$B$B<The captain looks almost sad and spits in disgust.>$B$BAlright, I know what we need to do. Or rather, what YOU need to do!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=5,`OfferRewardEmote2`=5,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11331;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Nicely done, $N, nicely done!$B$B<The captain seems beside himself with glee.>$B$BThat\'ll show those good-for-nothing Forsaken to think about messing with us!$B$BI\'d say you\'ve earned yourself something from the treasury!',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11332;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11335;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Prospector Belvar browses the book of runes.>$B$BHmm... there\'s so much here. I\'m going to need some time to study it, and if we hope to understand these runes, we\'ll need to try to make our own.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`CompleteEmote`=1 WHERE `entry`=11346;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'ve done well in defeating Binder Murdis, but the Iron Dwarves won\'t give up easily.$B$BWe\'ve made a lot of progress in understanding how they manipulate runes. Perhaps next time we encounter them, our knowledge will give us an advantage.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11348;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Belvar handles the tools carefully.>$B$BI\'m going to try these out. If we\'re to understand the Iron Dwarves\' motives and defeat them, I need to know exactly what the runes are doing.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`CompleteEmote`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11349;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Researcher Aderan listens to your findings.>$B$BThe runes for \"north\" and \"west\" appeared multiple times? There\'s a highly reinforced command to move in that direction, but the runes are more than propulsion. Something is attracting them, but what?',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1 WHERE `entry`=11355;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Aderan listens as you describe your findings.>$B$BOf course! This Megalith must be the key to the Iron Dwarves\' plans. We must destroy it before their plan comes to fruition!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11358;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'ve done well in felling Megalith, but I wonder about his final words.$B$BYou\'re sure he said the Stoneforge?$B$BI know of no place with that name, but it sounds like a word with origins in the titans. What plans do the Iron Dwarves have for such a thing? This bears watching, $N, for we must find it before the Iron Dwarves\' plan comes to fruition.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11359;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Nice shooting, ace.$B$BHere\'s your wages. Come back tomorrow for another round, ya hear?',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1 WHERE `entry`=11391;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='So the quartermaster sent you?$B$B<Gil seems relieved.>$B$BTo be honest, we\'re running a bit behind here and we\'re going to need some help making our goals.$B$B<Gil shudders.>$B$BNone of the men want to brave the wrath of Captain Adams.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11406;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11414;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Ulfang howls loudly at your defeat of his great eagle enemy.>$B$BThe honor of the kill is yours. I wish that it had been my maw to finally close upon her neck.$B$BLet us not waste the sacrifice that she has made for us. Here, eat them!',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11416;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent work, $N! You took out a good chunk of their dragon riders and really pissed off their leadership.$B$BAre you ready to head back to Valgarde and report the good news to Zorek? If so, I\'ve got a crazy idea!

',`OfferRewardEmote1`=4,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`OfferRewardEmote3`=6,`OfferRewardEmote4`=5,`CompleteEmote`=6,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11421;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Lieutenant Icehammer takes the harpoon control mechanism from you.>$B$BAh, you come bearing gifts!',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=5,`CompleteEmote`=6 WHERE `entry`=11427;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='My heart broke when I learned the keepers had turned against us. Once, we considered them our brothers and our closest friends.$B$BI grieve for the brothers and sisters we have lost, but without your help, there would be no hope for our future. You will always be welcome among us, $N.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11428;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='For the Alliance! You\'re a strong one, $N. Strong enough to crack some vrykul skull at Nifflevar.

',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`CompleteEmote`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11429;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11430;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You did what had to be done. Though some might consider it dishonorable to slay the helpless, in this case you would have been a fool to have done otherwise.$B$BAnd we certainly couldn\'t have just left them standing there to be ritually wakened, now could we?$B$BIt was a brave thing you did for all of us down in those catacombs, $N.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`RequestItemsText`='$N, I find it implausible that you have dealt with enough of the dormant vrykul. Come back when you have done so.',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11432;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='We\'re going to go places together, $N.  With my good looks and your... can-do attitude, we\'re sure to make a killing.',`RequestItemsText`='Did you obtain my relics, $N?  Nobody gets by in this life on good looks alone... not even me!',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11434;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You are insane, $N! What kind of degenerate would actually launch themselves from a harpoon gun as a method of travel?$B$BBut I guess you need to be a little crazy to pull off what you did up there on the bluffs! Fantastic work! We\'ve gotten word that the Dragonflayer leader, Ingvar, is furious! Maybe one day you\'ll be ready to stomp his face into the dirt - in the name of our beloved Alliance.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11436;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardEmote1`=2,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11451;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I\'m not sure that I like the sound of that one bit! The Lich King absconding with Ymiron can only mean trouble. Unfortunate that you weren\'t able to kill him along with his queen.$B$BStill, you\'ve put a huge dent in their plans and bought us the valuable time that we need.$B$BAnd who knows, with the way you get around, you\'ll likely run into King Ymiron again. I\'m sure that he won\'t fare so well the next time you meet.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=15,`OfferRewardEmote2`=1,`OfferRewardEmote3`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11452;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent work!  It might not be quite as daring as plundering the high seas, but I\'d be a darned son of a deckswabber if I passed on this opportunity.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=4,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11455;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I thank you, $N.  My people are in a time of great need.',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11456;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You continue to prove your worth as an ally, $N.  Your actions will not be forgotten.',`OfferRewardEmote1`=1,`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11457;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You are a formidable ally, $N.  My people will forever be in your debt.',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11458;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You didn\'t understand a thing Zeh\'gehn said?  Well, of course not.$B$BLet\'s see then.',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11459;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='A job well done.  Here\'s your cut, $N.  There\'s more where this came from.$B$BThere\'s no shortage of deadbeat pirates on this island.',`RequestItemsText`='You\'re back.  Did you get what\'s owed to me?',`DetailsEmote1`=4 WHERE `entry`=11464;
